Terminal chat application. The server is written in C++ and uses the socket API. The client is written in Python, and the TUI uses the Textual library. This is a toy project, and it is not safe for deployment yet. 

To run it:
<ol>
  <li>run Make in the src directory/li>
  <li>run the client executable in /src</li>
  <li>run python3 client-tui.py</li>
</ol>
